📅 3. datetime Module

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

🔹 What is datetime Module?

```text id="datetime_def"
The datetime module is used for working with dates and times.
```

---

📥 Import

```python id="import_datetime"
from datetime import datetime
```

---

💻 Current Date and Time

```python id="current_datetime"
from datetime import datetime

now = datetime.now()

print(now)
```

---

💻 Current Date

```python id="current_date"
from datetime import date

today = date.today()

print(today)
```

---

💻 Create Custom Date

```python id="custom_date"
from datetime import datetime

birthday = datetime(
    2003,
    10,
    5
)

print(birthday)
```

---

💻 Formatting Date

```python id="date_format"
from datetime import datetime

now = datetime.now()

print(
    now.strftime(
        "%d-%m-%Y"
    )
)
```

---

▶️ Sample Output

```text id="date_format_output"
10-06-2026
```

